Dialogue: 10,0:00:13.01,0:00:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hatsue!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:15.19,0:00:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Jump over the fire to me.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:17.73,0:00:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And... And we...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:14.93,0:01:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,W-We can't, after all!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:17.74,0:01:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:19.58,0:01:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I just decided. \NI want to marry you.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:24.25,0:01:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So... So we can't until then.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:32.48,0:01:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hatsue!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:59.08,0:02:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I found this at the beach this morning.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:02.74,0:02:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep it as a token of our promise.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:11.35,0:02:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll treasure it forever.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:33.39,0:02:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji—
Dialogue: 10,0:02:39.51,0:02:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:40.55,0:02:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:50.41,0:02:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:09.72,0:03:12.74,Thought,,0,0,0,,That's got to be Hatsue.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:19.07,0:03:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Chiyoko!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:21.07,0:03:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Chiyoko!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:25.26,0:03:26.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Chiyoko!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:27.85,0:03:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yasuo is here!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:31.22,0:03:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:34.88,0:03:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I was in the vicinity,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:36.45,0:03:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,so I thought I'd stop by and chat about good old Tokyo with you. {not sure where hisashiburi goes here since we literally saw them talking on the ferry at the end of the first part}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:43.40,0:03:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw her.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:45.55,0:03:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl Hatsue...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:48.90,0:03:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,She's gotten awfully close to Shinji.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:50.85,0:03:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:56.17,0:03:58.50,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Because the island's water supply is sparse,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:58.50,0:04:01.78,Narrator,,0,0,0,,one of the women's tasks is fetching water.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:35.52,0:04:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:38.37,0:04:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, it's you, {Kawamoto's }Yasuo?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:43.73,0:04:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I'd sneak up on you \Nto surprise you.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:46.67,0:04:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:49.78,0:04:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to see you about something.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:55.19,0:04:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:56.26,0:04:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, let's sit down \Nand talk without rushing.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:02.18,0:05:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better do what I say, \Nor you'll regret it.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:05.86,0:05:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:07.23,0:05:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,T-Take your hands off me!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:16.10,0:05:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't want me to tell everyone about you and Shinji,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:19.78,0:05:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,you'd better do what I say.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:21.72,0:05:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Me and Shinji? \NWhat's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:23.84,0:05:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't play dumb.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:25.31,0:05:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you jumped the gun on me \Nand got it on with Shinji! {to have a secret affair; to meet secretly and flirt with each other​}
Dialogue: 10,0:05:28.70,0:05:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be an idiot. \NWe haven't done anything.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:30.98,0:05:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I know the whole story.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:32.74,0:05:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What you and Shinji were doing\N on the mountain on the third.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:35.99,0:05:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,See, you're blushing.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:37.98,0:05:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can do the same thing with me!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:40.80,0:05:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Hatsue. Hatsue!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:46.80,0:05:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop struggling, Hatsue!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:49.71,0:05:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hatsue!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:54.40,0:05:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow-ow!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:04.00,0:06:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:06.26,0:06:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow-ow!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:21.06,0:06:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No, stop! \NWait! What are you doing?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:23.84,0:06:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I could get hurt!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:25.33,0:06:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down. I won't do it again. Okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:30.59,0:06:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hatsue, you're not going to tell your dad, are you? Are you?!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:36.42,0:06:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, please! I'll do anything! \NDon't tell him.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:42.70,0:06:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if you draw water and carry it\N to my house for me, I won't.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:47.15,0:06:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:48.81,0:06:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:50.48,0:06:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Uncle Teru's one scary bastard... {was mean}
Dialogue: 10,0:06:53.71,0:06:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, I'll do it!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:56.62,0:06:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll draw water or whatever you want!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:07.28,0:07:08.60,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The following day,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:08.60,0:07:13.64,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Shinji's brother Hiroshi was due back from his school trip.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:13.64,0:07:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You! Get back here! \NTaste my blade! {????????? no clue}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:21.51,0:07:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Shinji did what?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:24.24,0:07:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:25.32,0:07:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep, I'm sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:27.47,0:07:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,He sneaked around our backs\N and got a little taste of Hatsue.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:33.15,0:07:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:34.22,0:07:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That sly dog!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:35.88,0:07:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotta keep a close eye\N on our Shinji, don't you? {??? no idea what he says or how it's funny}
Dialogue: 10,0:07:44.89,0:07:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, how nice of you to buy\N your mom a souvenir.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:48.60,0:07:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:50.53,0:07:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, Mom...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:52.01,0:07:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,They're saying Shinji went and got a taste of Hatsue.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:55.41,0:07:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:57.84,0:08:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiroshi, who told you that?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:00.54,0:08:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody's saying it.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:03.19,0:08:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But what does "get a taste of" mean? {lit: do a pleasant/tasty thing}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:05.38,0:08:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Cretin!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:13.14,0:08:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Old man Miyata Teru must be goin' senile.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:16.83,0:08:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:18.60,0:08:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,He don't even know his daughter's lost her cherry.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:24.27,0:08:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji got it on with Hatsue, the sly dog.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:28.20,0:08:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Stupid old man Teru don't even know Shinji's made off with the goods! {???? nc what's that last part}
Dialogue: 10,0:08:39.35,0:08:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Whaddya think you're doin'?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:24.17,0:09:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:27.48,0:09:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you heard the nasty rumors
Dialogue: 10,0:09:30.67,0:09:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,about you and that girl?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:33.70,0:09:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you sleep with her?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:37.22,0:09:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't. I swear!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:44.85,0:09:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's good.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:48.34,0:09:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But be careful. \NRumors spread very quickly.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:54.15,0:09:57.06,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Because it was a small island,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:57.06,0:10:00.34,Narrator,,0,0,0,,the rumor spread quickly\N all over the town.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:02.92,0:10:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean she and Shinji did it already?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:10.53,0:10:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That Hatsue...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:25.12,0:10:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what she's thinking.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:26.56,0:10:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:31.50,0:10:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Miyata-san home?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:33.44,0:10:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Auntie? {mrs. kubo - silly to use mr/mrs in a japanese setting}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:35.85,0:10:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to talk to your father. \NWould you call him?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:39.08,0:10:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:56.93,0:11:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry... Father says he can't see you now.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:00.22,0:11:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Can't see me?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:10.64,0:11:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't want to see me\N because I'm a poor widow, is that it?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:15.11,0:11:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,My Shinji hasn't done anything \Nlike what those gossips are saying!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:21.11,0:11:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I came down here to tell him so!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:30.23,0:11:32.55,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The rumor that Hatsue has been
Dialogue: 10,0:11:32.55,0:11:35.88,Narrator,,0,0,0,,locked up in her home\N because of an affair with Shinji
Dialogue: 10,0:11:35.88,0:11:38.46,Narrator,,0,0,0,,has also reached Chiyoko.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:38.46,0:11:41.77,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Chiyoko, shocked by the consequences of the tales she spread,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:41.77,0:11:45.27,Narrator,,0,0,0,,is suffering deeply from her own act of jealousy.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:45.27,0:11:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:48.19,0:11:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, the lighthouse keeper's daughter?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:51.02,0:11:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You're up early.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:52.98,0:11:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going back to Tokyo today.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:56.29,0:11:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I came to say goodbye.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:00.99,0:12:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji, am I ugly?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:06.34,0:12:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I {\i1}am{\i0} ugly, aren't I?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:07.83,0:12:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:09.43,0:12:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You're beautiful!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:11.40,0:12:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:12.25,0:12:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you are.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:13.58,0:12:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji, we're leaving.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:18.26,0:12:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You are! You're beautiful!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:24.78,0:12:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You really are!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:31.06,0:12:35.59,Thought,,0,0,0,,Shinji said I was beautiful.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:36.77,0:12:39.57,Thought,,0,0,0,,Me, the ugly girl \Nwho told tales out of jealousy.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:48.02,0:12:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:51.13,0:12:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,This morning, when I went by Uncle Teru's house...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:01.21,0:13:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I was getting \Na love letter... at my age.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:05.30,0:13:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It thrilled me, for sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:08.28,0:13:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,But then I looked at it, \Nand it was for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:11.43,0:13:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So here you go.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:15.87,0:13:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:18.61,0:13:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm hurrying to write this\N while it's still dark out.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:24.61,0:13:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Since my father heard the rumor, \Nhe's keeping me in the house
Dialogue: 10,0:13:29.27,0:13:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,from the time you come\N home from fishing
Dialogue: 10,0:13:32.13,0:13:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,until you leave again in the morning.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:36.59,0:13:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm going to make him understand\N and let us be together someday.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:05.22,0:14:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:08.00,0:14:11.64,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Days passed before the two \Ncould see each other.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:12.47,0:14:15.38,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Suddenly, a new development occurred.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:15.83,0:14:21.37,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The captain of Terukichi's ship,\N the {\i1}Utajima-maru{\i0}, came to the island.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:21.37,0:14:23.56,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It was said he came to pick
Dialogue: 10,0:14:23.56,0:14:26.70,Narrator,,0,0,0,,two new members for his crew from the island's young men.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:30.47,0:14:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! Just like a head \Nof the youth committee oughta!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:33.16,0:14:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you got picked to be \Na crewman on the {\i1}Utajima-maru{\i0}!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:39.65,0:14:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it wasn't really my idea\N to go on the ship,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:43.11,0:14:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,but since Uncle Miyata Teru wants me to, I guess I'd better!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:49.61,0:14:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So who's the other guy?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:52.34,0:14:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot, you think I know that?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:54.86,0:14:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji, I heard from the captain. \NI'm real happy for you.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:59.08,0:15:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about the fishing. \NWe can handle it ourselves.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:02.58,0:15:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Go on and take the offer.\N It'll be good for your future.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:12.84,0:15:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I'd be happy to work for you, sir!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:18.75,0:15:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's decided, then!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:20.31,0:15:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, now I see why Teru told me \Nyou'd make a good sailor.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:24.81,0:15:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:25.73,0:15:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,When I mentioned your name,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:28.37,0:15:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,he agreed without a moment's thought \Nthat it should be you.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:50.48,0:15:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Auntie!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:58.76,0:15:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:00.56,0:16:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you please give this to Shinji?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:12.33,0:16:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I won't be gone long,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:15.39,0:16:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,but please take care \Nof the youth committee for me.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:18.58,0:16:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:20.90,0:16:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:33.85,0:16:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji, hurry up!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:57.80,0:17:02.31,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The {\i1}Utajima-maru{\i0} has docked at a port in Okinawa
Dialogue: 10,0:17:02.31,0:17:05.00,Narrator,,0,0,0,,in order to load scraps.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:06.19,0:17:09.92,Radio,,0,0,0,,The typhoon front, brewing near Ishigaki Island,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:09.92,0:17:14.43,Radio,,0,0,0,,is growing stronger and is expected\N to cross the Okinawa mainland soon,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:14.43,0:17:17.59,Radio,,0,0,0,,so all ships in the area are advised \Nto steer out of the way.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:17.59,0:17:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no! It's heading straight for the {\i1}Utajima-maru{\i0}!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:05.02,0:18:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What? We lost the mooring line? {meaning they were moored in the port I guess? although that thing they tie the lifeline to seems to be floating and more like a buoy so idk}
Dialogue: 10,0:18:06.94,0:18:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! What'll we do, Captain?!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:08.94,0:18:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,They said the typhoon\N peaked at one o'clock.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:11.60,0:18:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,If we can tie a mooring line now, \Nwe'll make it.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:18.95,0:18:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I have any volunteers \Nto go tie the mooring line?!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:26.96,0:18:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,No one at all?!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:29.62,0:18:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You cowards.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:32.98,0:18:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:34.75,0:18:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do it!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:35.88,0:18:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, go for it!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:38.79,0:18:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best, Shinji.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:22.89,0:19:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll be fine, I'm sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:24.99,0:19:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He's just like his late father.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:27.20,0:19:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,He once swam around this island five times. He swims like a fish.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:48.38,0:19:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,He did it! We're saved! Tie the rope!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:02.19,0:20:06.10,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Shinji's feat was reported by radio.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:06.10,0:20:10.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Even before he returned,\N it became the new hot topic in town.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:25.95,0:20:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:28.79,0:20:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hatsue!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:32.59,0:20:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:39.57,0:20:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, look at the lovebirds!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:44.50,0:20:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who's gonna marry her.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:48.56,0:20:50.88,Narrator,,0,0,0,,After receiving Chiyoko's letter from Tokyo,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:50.88,0:20:53.34,Narrator,,0,0,0,,the keeper's wife understood the real story
Dialogue: 10,0:20:53.34,0:20:58.61,Narrator,,0,0,0,,and decided to speak to Miyata Terukichi\N on behalf of Shinji and Hatsue.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:58.61,0:21:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already decided \Nwho Hatsue will marry.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:01.61,0:21:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, we heard.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:04.41,0:21:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But Hatsue loves Shinji, not Yasuo.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:08.62,0:21:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I'm saying!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:10.35,0:21:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji's going to be my son-in-law.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:14.27,0:21:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked the captain to find out \Nwhich man was best.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:21.38,0:21:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And you know the result.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:25.40,0:21:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,A man's gotta be strong!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:27.45,0:21:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:28.64,0:21:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji's the kind of man \Nwho's got that strength.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:39.40,0:21:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,When I'm twenty, I'll get a seaman's competency certificate.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:43.77,0:21:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to be a sailor \Njust like my old man was.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:48.66,0:21:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we can get married, all right?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:55.41,0:21:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember this?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:57.47,0:21:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.72,0:22:37.41,Song,,0,0,0,,I write a letter to my loved one
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.30,0:22:44.52,Song,,0,0,0,,I write and tear it, tear it, and write again
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.52,0:22:51.11,Song,,0,0,0,,I throw the rolled up paper at the window {meaning at the glass, probably as a distraction}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.11,0:22:58.15,Song,,0,0,0,,It's raining outside, just like the tears on my cheeks
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.39,0:23:06.21,Song,,0,0,0,,Life is a sea, youth is a boat
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.21,0:23:13.29,Song,,0,0,0,,My love, please come and save me
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.29,0:23:15.43,Song,,0,0,0,,S.O.S.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.59,0:23:19.41,Song,,0,0,0,,S.O.S.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.41,0:23:26.98,Song,,0,0,0,,I feel like I'm sinking
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.98,0:23:36.50,Song,,0,0,0,,Not a single star in sight, in the sea of ​​sadness
